narration_text: #C C throws a paper in the bin
#C C holds the handle of a cooking pot
#C C picks up the cooking pot with noodles
#C C pours the noodles in a bowl
#C C places the cooking pot in a kitchen sink
#C C stirs the noodles in the bowl
#C C picks up a cooking pan with vegetables
#C C pours the vegetables on the bowl of noodles
#C C stirs the bowl with chopsticks
#C C places the cooking pan in the kitchen sink
#C C places the chopsticks on the cooking pan
#C C places the towel on the kitchen surface
